{
  "stem": "24409.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We made an appointment with the chief of police, which was granted because we said we would help him to get rid of the people who had come illegally into to Hungary, and whom he had in jails.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had many dozens who had come illegally from Poland, and from Czechoslovakia, into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Fled into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in Hungary they had no means to support, and no papers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They brought them to jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Hungary didn't like to feed them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The same was true in Romania and in Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All the other countries wanted to get rid of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Particularly, of the refugees who had no money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Which we used in order to-- we used by promising him that if he let our ships past, that we will take a certain number of Jews from the prison.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And Kalman got his appointment because he said, here's a plan to get rid of all those Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We made it as  far as the anteroom of the chief of police.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We never saw him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But his executive officer came back, said what is it, and I told him the story.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That I want to make myself consul of Liberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it will take months before this is found out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the meanwhile, [INAUDIBLE] many ships will go, and on every ship we will take 50 or 70, I don't remember the number of Jews anymore, which we will take from his prisons.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went into the chief of police, and I don't know anymore, how long he's gone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't seem to me a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At least I don't remember it as a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came out and said, that Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-and-so does not know anything, does not want to know anything, but you told him.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
